Did aliens mingle with ancient civilizations? Thousands of years before crashing in Roswell, did aliens interact with humans? ANCIENT ALIENS reviews the evidence left in countries around the world.

 Is there a reason that so many structures in many different lands all point to the same spot in thesky? Did these invaders have an influence on early science? Ancient text refer to flying objects and emissaries from the gods. Are these fanciful leaps of faith or hard evidence of otherworldly races? Peer past the speculation and discover what science and history have to say about ANCIENT ALIENS.
